The aims of this study are to: 1.

 explore supportive care needs in colorectal cancer patients with treatment and survivors; 2.

 compare the supportive care needs in different stage of colorectal cancer; 3.

 identify the significant factors for the supportive care needs; 4.

 explore the supportive care needs within one year after newly diagnosis.

